OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother dry and bright day with
OL,6,Flong periods of sunshine. A chilly
OL,7,Fstart with low cloud around the coast.
OL,8,FBecoming quite warm inland by the
OL,9,Fafternoon but cooler along the coast
OL,10,Fwith patchy low cloud and mist in
OL,11,Fplaces.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry with some evening
OL,14,Fsunshine to start with, but low cloud
OL,15,Fand mist gradually returning from the
OL,16,Fcoast. Cloud spreading further south
OL,17,Fand west overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
