OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FMainly dry on Saturday but
OL,6,Frather cloudy with the odd spot of
OL,7,Frain possible in the morning. A much
OL,8,Fcooler day than Friday.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FVariable
OL,11,Fcloud and bright spells on Sunday and
OL,12,FMonday with some showery outbreaks of
OL,13,Frain and turning a little warmer
OL,14,Fagain. Mostly dry Tuesday but quite
OL,15,Fcool and cloudy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
